## 🎬 Tu Primera Animación

```elixir
Kino.animate(0, fn contador ->
  frame = Kino.Markdown.new("""
  <div style="background-color: #667eea; padding: 40px; text-align: center; color: white; border-radius: 15px;">
    <h1 style="font-size: 80px;">#{contador}</h1>
    <p>Contador animado</p>
  </div>
  """)

  Process.sleep(1000)
  {:cont, frame, contador + 1}
end)
```

## 🌈 Animación de Colores

```elixir
colores = ["#ff6b6b", "#4ecdc4", "#45b7d1", "#f9ca24", "#6c5ce7"]

Kino.animate(0, fn indice ->
  color = Enum.at(colores, rem(indice, length(colores)))

  frame = Kino.Markdown.new("""
  <div style="background-color: #{color}; padding: 60px; border-radius: 20px; text-align: center;">
    <h1 style="font-size: 100px; color: white;">✨</h1>
  </div>
  """)

  Process.sleep(500)
  {:cont, frame, indice + 1}
end)
```

